text: Ahmed Bamsaud (, born 22 November 1995) is a Saudi Arabian professional footballer who plays as a left back or left winger for Pro League side Al- Fayha. ==Career== Bamsaud he started his career at the youth team of Al-Hilal . and he signed a one-year contract with Al-Fayha on loan from Al-Hilal on June 20, 2017 . Bamsaud left Al-Hilal and joined Pro League side Al-Fayha on June 5, 2018 . and renewed his contract with Al-Fayha for 2-years on January 30, 2020 . ==References== == External links == * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Saudi Arabian footballers Category:Saudi Arabia youth international footballers Category:Al Hilal SFC players Category:Al-Fayha FC players Category:Saudi Professional League players Category:Prince Mohammad bin Salman League players Category:Association football fullbacks Category:Association football wingers
